                     <interp inst="t18220417-219-off1154" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing on the <rs id="t18220417-219-cd1155" type="crimeDate">21st of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-219-off1154 t18220417-219-cd1155"></join>, three waistcoats, value 2 s.; two gowns, value 18 s.; six frocks, value 6 s.; three bed gowns, value 18 s.; one mantle, value 1 s.; four shirts, value 10 d.; five caps, value 2 d., and two pair of gloves, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220417-219-victim1973" type="victimName">
